**Term insurance** provides a death benefit to your family if you die during the policy term — at very low premiums compared to traditional life insurance. A ₹1 crore term policy typically costs ₹700–1,000/month for a 30-year-old non-smoker. The critical question is: how much cover do you actually need? This calculator computes it based on your income replacement needs and liabilities.
